wiki.content: 530 is the 7th track from VULTURES 2. This track was first revealed under the name of “The Cars Missing” on an early tracklist for Donda 2 that surfaced on February 4, 2022. The song later made an appearance on the first tracklist Kanye West shared himself on February 18, as “530.” Finally, it appeared as “Dear Summer” on the February 22 setlist for the Miami listening party for the album, shared by Ben Baller on the same night. This song was first previewed at the start of Ye’s short documentary, LAST WEEK, released on October 10, 2022. The snippet showcased a reference track in the background of Ye’s rapping and some mumbled lyrics. The track was eventually released on the 3rd of August 2024, still containing the mumble lyrics. A week later, an updated version released replacing Ye's bridge with Ty Dolla $ign. A final update was released on the 11th of November 2024 which contained a completely redone second half with complete lyrics done by AI. Read more on Last.fm.
